{"tid":2207404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12港人送中︱國際特赦組織發起聯署 促中國確保被扣人士不受酷刑 安排與家屬會面","createTime":"2020-09-18T06:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T16:59:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca5c4c0b90fa6b91143de3bf44e5b88f951f0cb","tid":2207404,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AmnestyHK/posts/10158350191786273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAmnestyHK%2Fposts%2F10158350191786273&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=2a7b1c80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AmnestyHK/posts/10158350191786273</a><br />\n<br />\n12名港人被送中將近一個月，至今音訊全無。國際特赦組織香港分會發起聯署，要求中國當局確保12人可盡快與家屬及由家屬委託的律師定期會面，並確保12人都不會遭受酷刑或不人道對待等。<br />\n<br />\n12名港人自上月23日，被中國當局以涉嫌觸犯偷越國（邊）境罪，拘留在深圳鹽田區看守所至今，一直與外界隔絕，未能與家人及按12人或其家人意願委託的律師聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織香港分會今日發起網上聯署，指12人「正面臨遭受酷刑或其他不人道對待的即時威脅」，故要求中國當局確保12人可盡快與家屬，及由家屬委託的律師進行定期和有效的會面，並且確保12人不會遭受酷刑或其他不人道對待，以及讓12人按其要求或需要，盡快得到定期、不受限制的醫療照顧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/OPXA5VK2LZD7HGY7F7IK4VD27Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FOPXA5VK2LZD7HGY7F7IK4VD27Y%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=318662c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FOPXA5VK2LZD7HGY7F7IK4VD27Y%2F&h=87777049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/OPXA5VK2LZD7HGY7F7IK4VD27Y/</a>"},{"pid":"57ec091692e001a2464e70f4c86fad9888b84889","tid":2207404,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef5a0c676ab0b